name: 01. Create a new account with profile information in vehicle's info slide
fullName: Onboarding feature: 01. Create a new account with profile information in vehicle's info slide

steps.name: Given I navigate to the create an account button in the menu
When I submit email password and profile information
And The get started button is displayed in vehicle's info slide
And I allow notifications
And The app should display My Garage screen
Then I should be logged in
